ople spend less on ads. Local agencies in Ranchi can run targeted campaigns for less money, which means a higher return on investment (ROI) and less risk of trade disruptions.</p></details>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    <p>© Global Webify | Written by Iftekhar</p>', '../../assets/images/content/blog/U.S.–China Trade War 2.0 Is Shaking Up Global Digital Marketing.image.jpg', 1, 'published', NULL, '[\"US\\u2013China Trade War\",\"Digital Marketing in India\",\"AI Tools for Marketing\",\"SEO Trends 2025\",\"Marketing Strategy\",\"Global Webify\",\"Ranchi Businesses\",\"Ad Campaign Optimization\",\"Social Media Marketing\",\"Data Privacy\",\"Marketing Challenges\",\"Economic Trends\"]', '2025-10-23 10:12:57', '2025-10-24 17:36:29', 'IT Industry Trends, Digital Transformation, Digital Marketing, Business Growth, Technology & Innovation,  Digital Marketing, Global Business Trends, AI & Technology, SEO Strategies,'),
