(6, 'How Global Webify Improved SEO Rankings for 100+ Clients in 2025', 'how-global-webify-improved-seo-rankings-for-100-clients-in-2025', 'A behind-the-scenes look at our proven SEO strategies that helped over 100 businesses reach Google’s first page.', 'In the first half of 2025, Global Webify achieved a major milestone — successfully improving the search engine rankings of 100+ clients. Using a blend of technical SEO, content strategy, and backlink building, our SEO team ensured measurable ROI and online visibility for businesses across various industries.', 'assets/images/content/news/news_4590468-2433706_1754379647.jpg', 'General', '[\"seo\",\"rankings\",\"marketing\",\"growth\"]', 'published', '2025-08-05 04:10:47', 0, 1, 364, '2025-08-05 07:40:47', '2026-01-05 12:44:01'),
