(2, 'Digital Marketing', 'We don’t do one-size-fits-all marketing. At Global Webify, we focus on digital strategies that actually put your brand in front of the people who matter. Whether you’re operating out of Ranchi or looking to expand into the UK, our campaigns are designed to reach the right audience at exactly the right moment. From boosting your SEO to managing your social presence, we’re here to make sure your brand stands out—no matter the market. If you need a digital marketing plan that keeps your business top of mind, you’re in the right place. Our team’s ready to make it happen.', 'Get Started', 'digital-marketing', '/assets/images/services/digital-marketing.avif', 2, 1, '2025-07-29 05:21:48', '2025-09-11 07:41:48'),
