(7, 'Neeraj Patel', NULL, NULL, 'Excellent experience working with Global Webify! They designed a stunning website for my business that perfectly captures my brand\'s vision. Their professionalism, attention to detail, and timely delivery exceeded my expectations. Highly recommend their services for anyone looking for a talented and reliable web designer. Five stars isn\'t enough – they\'re truly top-notch!', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/testimonial_1753174764_687f52ec574d4.png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-08-04 10:25:28', '2025-08-21 05:10:19', 1, 'active', 'Omni Overseas', NULL, ''),
(9, 'Nirav Khatri', NULL, NULL, 'I\'m extremely satisfied with the website created by Global Webify! The team was professional, responsive, and truly understood my vision. They delivered a clean, user-friendly, and visually appealing site that exceeded my expectations. Highly recommend their services to anyone looking for reliable and high-quality web development.', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/testimonial_1753174888_687f53686dde5.png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-08-04 10:29:15', '2025-09-11 11:30:18', 1, 'active', 'Treezio', NULL, ''),
(10, 'padmacourier14', NULL, NULL, 'I recently availed digital marketing services from Global Webify, and I must say, the experience has been exceptional! Their team is highly professional, knowledgeable, and dedicated to delivering results.\r\n\r\nFrom SEO to social media marketing and paid advertising, they provided a comprehensive strategy tailored to my business needs. Within just a few months, I noticed a significant increase in website traffic, better engagement on social media, and a boost in overall brand visibility.\r\n\r\nWhat sets Global Webify apart is their commitment to transparency and communication. They provided regular performance reports, insightful recommendations, and were always available to address any queries. Their expertise in the latest digital marketing trends truly helped my business grow.\r\n\r\nI highly recommend Global Webify to anyone looking for effective and result-driven digital marketing solutions. Their services are worth every penny!', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed-6.png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-08-04 10:30:17', '2025-09-11 11:29:21', 1, 'active', 'Website Development', NULL, ''),
(11, 'Babita Kumari', NULL, NULL, 'I just got my business website set up by GlobalWebify, and honestly, the whole process was super easy. Their ₹4,999 deal is perfect if you’re just starting out—doesn’t break the bank or anything. The team was always quick to reply (which, let’s be real, is rare), and they actually finished the site when they said they would.', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (7).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:23:02', '2025-09-11 11:30:59', 3, 'active', 'Website Development', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
(12, 'Suman Mahalder', NULL, NULL, '\"I was impressed by Global Webify\'s creative approach to web design. They took the time to understand my brand and developed a custom solution that exceeded my expectations. Their team is talented, and their prices are competitive. Great value for the quality delivered!\"', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (8).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:23:54', '2025-09-03 12:23:54', 4, 'active', 'Client', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
(13, 'Y k101', NULL, NULL, 'I had an amazing experience working with Global Webify! Their team is professional, responsive, and truly knowledgeable. They helped redesign my website, and the results exceeded my expectations. Very Thankful to Them\r\n\r\nWhat impressed me most was their ability to understand my business needs and translate them into a functional and visually stunning website. Communication was seamless throughout the process, and they always delivered on time.\r\n\r\nI highly recommend Global Webify for anyone looking for top-notch web design, development, and digital marketing services. Thank you for your outstanding work!', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (9).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:24:45', '2025-09-03 12:24:45', 5, 'active', 'Client', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
(14, 'Md Shahbaz', NULL, NULL, 'I just worked with Global Webify on a website development project, and I\'m really pleased with the outcome! Their team\'s professionalism, inventiveness, and technological know-how were outstanding from the start.\r\n\r\nAfter taking the time to comprehend my idea, they created an amazing, user-friendly website that surpassed my expectations. The website runs rapidly on all devices, has a sleek, contemporary appearance, and operates well.\r\n\r\nTheir promptness and commitment to producing high-quality work on schedule were what most impressed me. They gave me frequent updates along the process and were always ready to address my inquiries.\r\n\r\nTo anyone searching for a trustworthy and knowledgeable web development partner, I heartily recommend Global Webify. I appreciate you creating my webpage.', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (10).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:25:33', '2025-09-03 12:25:33', 6, 'active', 'Client', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
(15, 'Leela Mor', NULL, NULL, 'Best company in website development in India as well as international level service providers in the aforesaid it related services. Co operative team ... always. Resolving issues immediately.', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (11).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:26:28', '2025-09-11 11:31:22', 7, 'active', 'Website Development', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
(16, 'Sagar Kumar', NULL, NULL, 'Great design team and quick turn around on all projects and request. With their help we have improved our google search results. My company has depended on them for quite sometime now and we have been doing business with them for a years. Their web design team is very knowledgeable and they always let us know when a new Google update is coming up before anyone even knows. If you want a reliable Web Design Company all them! I recommend 100%', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (12).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:27:13', '2025-09-03 12:27:13', 8, 'active', 'Client', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
(17, 'Prabir Malakar', NULL, NULL, 'I\'ve been working with Global Webify for a few months now, and I\'m impressed with their professionalism and expertise. They\'ve helped me improve my website\'s visibility and drive more traffic. Great job!\"', NULL, 'assets/images/testimonials/unnamed (13).png', 5, 0, 1, '2025-09-03 12:27:59', '2025-09-03 12:27:59', 9, 'active', 'Client', NULL, 'fas fa-code'),
